{"tid":2315374,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"騰訊 Tencent 與 Spotify 正式宣佈互持彼此至多 10% 股權","createTime":"2020-12-07T06:55:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T06:30:53.000Z","uid":122989,"like":5,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"e740d7d747d988691ca437388c3a84eef30263df","tid":2315374,"uid":122989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:55:09.000Z","msg":"來自中國的騰訊 Tencent 於今年初便釋出希望能夠收購全球最大音樂串流平台 Spotify 的計畫，藉以擴大其旗下 TME 音樂串流平台的影響力，然而並未如願。不過就在稍早，騰訊 Tencent 與 Spotify 正式宣佈雙方將互相持有少於 10% 的股權，意味著在某種程度上雙方已成為合作夥伴關係，無不讓音樂串流平台用戶排名中間的 Apple Music（Spotify 排名第一、TME 排名第三）感受到極大威脅。<br />\n<br />\n之所以會做出此一決策，除了騰訊 Tencent 因為整合了 QQ 音樂、酷狗音樂和酷我音樂，致使 TME 成為極具影響力的音樂串流平台之外，Spotify 近年來雖然營收持續成長，但是虧損也同步擴大，主因來自於高昂的音樂版權費用。對此，獲得了騰訊 Tencent 的支持，可以讓 Spotify 在金流難關上獲得一定程度的緩解。Spotify 創辦人兼執行長 Daniel Ek 在聲明中如此說道：「Spotify 與 TME 均看好全球音樂流媒體市場，這將使我們的用戶、藝人、音樂和業務合作夥伴帶來可觀的未來，這次交易將使兩家公司同時受惠於全球音樂串流媒體市場的成長利益。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2020/12/spotify-and-tencent-to-swap-10-percents-stakes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2020%2F12%2Fspotify-and-tencent-to-swap-10-percents-stakes&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYThR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=fd9f65b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2020/12/spotify-and-tencent-to-swap-10-percents-stakes</a>"},{"pid":"824c7e2681bfd2f66960437b3eb0d40ee9968390","tid":2315374,"uid":122989,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:55:39.000Z","msg":"unsub了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a64dbe0458fcedf6df9c6d9bc43b59273eb0c2b","tid":2315374,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"824c7e2681bfd2f66960437b3eb0d40ee9968390","tid":2315374,"uid":122989,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:55:39.000Z","msg":"unsub了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:56:31.000Z","msg":"+1